data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. HUGE PRICE ADJUSTMENT!!! LOOK NO FURTHER THIS CORNER LOT, 3 BEDROOM, 2 BATH, 2 CAR OVERSIZED-GARAGE, POOL HOME HAS IT ALL!!! This one-of-a-kind home was recently renovated including luxury vinyl flooring throughout (which if you prefer is covering gorgeous Terrazzo floors).. METAL ROOF 2019, HVAC 2017, Plumbing repiped throughout, Newer hybrid heat pump/water heater,  Newer variable speed pool pump, and a PAID OFF Solar System for years of free electricity giving you a low bill with the power company.  A Beautiful open-concept Kitchen with granite countertops, and solid-wood cabinets lends itself to culinary arts and entertaining !!!  You will love the split floorplan, with the kitchen and living room separating the bedrooms.  You will live the best Florida life walking out to your covered patio and a fully bird-caged in ground pool with diving board!!!  There is also plenty of space for your RV or Boat with gate access in the back corner of the property.  Don't miss your chance to have it all!!!
